burlap.domain.singleagent.mountaincar

Class MountainCarVisualizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.domain.singleagent.mountaincar.MountainCarVisualizer

  • public class MountainCarVisualizer
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for creating a Visualizer for a MountainCar Domain. The agent will be drawn as a red square and the shape of the hill in a black line.
